      "components": [
        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-midnight-ink:#000710;--color-action-orange:#ff5900;--color-primary-text:#000000;--color-paper-white:#ffffff;--color-soft-gray:#f3f3f7;--color-muted-slate:#b9bbc6;--color-cool-stone:#60646c;--color-ash-gray:#6f737b;--font-inter:system-ui,sans-serif;--font-flecha:serif;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:var(--font-inter);background:var(--color-paper-white);padding:48px 40px;width:600px;\">\n  <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--color-action-orange);margin:0 0 12px 0;letter-spacing:0.02em;text-transform:uppercase;\">⚡ Limited time offer</p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-family:var(--font-flecha);font-size:36px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.11;color:var(--color-primary-text);margin:0 0 8px 0;\">Finance built for speed and control.</h2>\n  <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;color:var(--color-cool-stone);margin:0 0 28px 0;\">Modern cards, banking, expenses, accounting, and more — in 120+ countries.</p>\n  <div style=\"display:flex;gap:0;align-items:stretch;border:1.5px solid #d1d1d8;border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--color-paper-white);\">\n    <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Enter your work email\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:15px;color:#15191e;background:transparent;border:none;outline:none;padding:14px 16px;flex:1;min-width:0;\" />\n    <button style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-paper-white);background:var(--color-action-orange);border:none;border-radius:0 4px 4px 0;padding:14px 24px;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;\">Get started</button>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:20px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;\">\n    <span style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;border:1.5px solid var(--color-action-orange);\">\n      <svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#ff5900\"/><polygon points=\"4.5,4 8.5,6 4.5,8\" fill=\"white\"/></svg>\n    </span>\n    <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:var(--color-action-orange);text-decoration:none;\">See Brex in action</a>\n  </div>\n</div>",
          "name": "Email Signup CTA Bar",
          "role": "",
          "description": ""
        },
        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-midnight-ink:#000710;--color-action-orange:#ff5900;--color-primary-text:#000000;--color-paper-white:#ffffff;--color-soft-gray:#f3f3f7;--color-muted-slate:#b9bbc6;--color-cool-stone:#60646c;--color-ash-gray:#6f737b;--font-inter:system-ui,sans-serif;--font-flecha:serif;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:var(--font-inter);background:var(--color-soft-gray);padding:48px 24px;width:600px;\">\n  <h2 style=\"font-family:var(--font-flecha);font-size:36px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.11;color:var(--color-primary-text);text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px 0;\">The card is just the start.</h2>\n  <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;color:var(--color-cool-stone);text-align:center;margin:0 0 36px 0;\">Everything you need to boost spending power and control — and eliminate manual work.</p>\n  <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;\">\n    <div style=\"background:var(--color-paper-white);border-radius:12px;padding:24px;\">\n      <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-primary-text);margin:0 0 8px 0;\">Corporate cards</p>\n      <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;color:var(--color-cool-stone);margin:0 0 20px 0;\">Spend smart globally with powerful cards and built-in controls.</p>\n      <div style=\"width:100%;height:80px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1a2e 60%,#2d2d44 100%);border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\">\n        <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--color-paper-white);letter-spacing:0.06em;\">BREX</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:var(--color-paper-white);border-radius:12px;padding:24px;\">\n      <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-primary-text);margin:0 0 8px 0;\">Expense management</p>\n      <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;color:var(--color-cool-stone);margin:0 0 20px 0;\">Use AI to automate approvals and reports. Track all spend in one place.</p>\n      <div style=\"background:var(--color-soft-gray);border-radius:8px;padding:12px;\">\n        <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:8px;\">\n          <div style=\"width:32px;height:22px;background:#e8eaf6;border-radius:4px;\"></div>\n          <div>\n            <div style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#15191e;\">JetBlue Travel</div>\n            <div style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:11px;color:var(--color-cool-stone);\">SOFTWARE</div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"margin-left:auto;font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#15191e;\">$305.21</div>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;\">\n          <div style=\"width:32px;height:22px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:4px;\"></div>\n          <div>\n            <div style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#15191e;\">Google Cloud</div>\n            <div style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:11px;color:var(--color-cool-stone);\">SOFTWARE</div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"margin-left:auto;font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#15191e;\">$1,240.00</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:var(--color-paper-white);border-radius:12px;padding:24px;\">\n      <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-primary-text);margin:0 0 8px 0;\">Bill pay</p>\n      <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;color:var(--color-cool-stone);margin:0 0 20px 0;\">AI-powered payment processing. Pay vendors on time, every time.</p>\n      <div style=\"background:var(--color-soft-gray);border-radius:8px;padding:12px;\">\n        <div style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:11px;color:var(--color-cool-stone);margin-bottom:4px;\">BALANCE DUE</div>\n        <div style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:#15191e;\">$20,512.86</div>\n        <div style=\"margin-top:10px;background:#e6f4ea;border-radius:4px;padding:4px 8px;display:inline-block;\">\n          <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#2e7d32;\">✓ Paid successfully</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:var(--color-paper-white);border-radius:12px;padding:24px;\">\n      <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-primary-text);margin:0 0 8px 0;\">Banking and treasury</p>\n      <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;color:var(--color-cool-stone);margin:0 0 20px 0;\">Save, spend, and grow your cash with up to 3.68%† — from day one.</p>\n      <div style=\"background:var(--color-soft-gray);border-radius:8px;padding:12px;\">\n        <div style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:11px;color:var(--color-cool-stone);margin-bottom:4px;\">INTEREST EARNED</div>\n        <div style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:#15191e;\">$608.90</div>\n        <div style=\"height:32px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#ff5900 0%,#ff8c42 100%);border-radius:4px;margin-top:10px;opacity:0.18;\"></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
